import React from 'react'; import { ShoppingCart, Plus, Minus, Trash2, ArrowRight } from 'lucide-react'; import { Link } from '../componentsRouter'; import { useApp } from '../contexts/AppContext'; const CartPage = () => { const { cart, updateCartQuantity, removeFromCart, navigate } = useApp(); const total = cart.reduce((sum, item) => sum + (item.price * item.quantity), 0); if (cart.length === 0) { return (

Your cart is empty

Add some products to get started

Browse Products
); } return (

Shopping Cart

{cart.map(item => (

{item.name}

Rp {item.price.toLocaleString('id-ID')}
{item.quantity}
Rp {(item.price * item.quantity).toLocaleString('id-ID')}
))}

Order Summary

Subtotal Rp {total.toLocaleString('id-ID')}
Shipping Rp 50,000
Total Rp {(total + 50000).toLocaleString('id-ID')}
); }; export default CartPage;
